                        <li><span style="background-color: #ffffff;">We require all third parties to respect the security of your personal data and to treat it in accordance with the law. We do not allow our third-party service providers to use your personal data for their own purposes and only permit them to process your personal data for specified purposes and in accordance with our instructions and the law.</span><span style="color: #000000;">&nbsp;</span></li>
